{"about_the_game":"The Coffee Queen is missing! The islanders seem to have forgotten her presence. You, the niece of the Coffee Queen need to <strong>uncover special recipes, brew drinks, serve them and transport islanders to their destinations</strong> to gather pieces of her memory. Only then can the Brewed Horizons can go back to its time of peace and quiet!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911630/extras/Wishlist_Now.gif?t=1739790351\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore the Brewed Horizons</h2>Explore and travel between the islands, collecting items and passengers!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> \ud83d\udc51 Use the Queen\u2019s old boat to travel between archipelagos.<br></li><li> \ud83d\udea2 Upgrade the boat with new sails, stronger hulls, and magical enhancements to overcome natural and supernatural obstacles.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Serve Special Beverages</h2>Wait! The islanders need to remember the Coffee Queen to reunite. Trigger key memories related to the Queen, and maybe even discover her disappearance.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> \ud83c\udfdd\ufe0f Collect unique ingredients from each archipelago.<br></li><li> \ud83c\udf79 Craft special beverages that trigger memories of the Coffee Queen and restore unity among the islanders.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defeat Monsters</h2>The disappearance of the Queen has spawned monsters in the sea!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> \u2694\ufe0f Use crafted items creatively to defeat the monsters.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Furnish and Decorate</h2>Ensure the comfort of the islanders, of course.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> \ud83e\ude91 Create safe and familiar environments for passengers according to their preferences.</li></ul><br>The fate of the Brewed Horizons lies in your hands. Are you ready to rise to the challenge and restore the kingdom to its former glory?","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepage